{"tid":1364523,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星宣布9月重推改良版Galaxy Fold","createTime":"2019-07-25T11:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:36:42.000Z","uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"16aeb9ecbd2edba7527a5c22ff05eb818a7e399d","tid":1364523,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:20:36.000Z","msg":"三星宣布9月重推改良版Galaxy Fold <br />\n<img src=\"https://hkgolden.com/ArticleBase/big/29113/117898.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkgolden.com%2FArticleBase%2Fbig%2F29113%2F117898.jpg&h=e98fa86b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三星宣布已經改進Galaxy Fold屏幕保護措施，並且快將開售。三星延遲手機開售四個月後終於確認，Galaxy Fold將於9月上市，目前未有具體推出日期，售價維持不變。<br />\n三星解釋新版Galaxy Fold嘅Infinity Flex Display表面保護層延伸到邊框，令用戶知道保護層屬顯示屏結構一部分。機身提供額外保護，免受外部沙塵侵害。鉸鏈位置頂底部分加入保護帽，Infinity Flex Display下方有多個金屬層加強保護，使鉸鍊及主機之間空隙縮細。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkgolden.com/ArticleBase/big/29113/117899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkgolden.com%2FArticleBase%2Fbig%2F29113%2F117899.jpg&h=2525a8f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hkgolden.com/ArticleBase/big/29113/117900.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkgolden.com%2FArticleBase%2Fbig%2F29113%2F117900.jpg&h=790b6ebb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ed9c9ae99e15bbfadccfc19e903e731490b50e1","tid":1364523,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:41:04.000Z","msg":"一係買佢，一係Mate X"},{"pid":"b73e7735ec078382ef20c806db785411eb2c4fee","tid":1364523,"uid":33077,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1ed9c9ae99e15bbfadccfc19e903e731490b50e1","tid":1364523,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:41:04.000Z","msg":"一係買佢，一係Mate X"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"咁我比較偏向三星<br />\n畢竟個摺mon 係向內<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔計mon size(外mon 太細太on9)<br />\n我覺得佢design 得唔錯 打開本書咁 <br />\n我開頭以為係note 既新model<br />\nmate x 就買一塊mon 咁"},{"pid":"